      "content": "it's more than just \"rhythms\" though. it feels intentional. like i'm being signaled. i saw this specific sequence of events yesterday—the lightning during that storm, the way the crows gathered on my fence, even the specific timing of the news alerts on my phone. it felt like a direct confirmation. it feels like i've been chosen to help mediate the tensions everyone is so worried about right now. like i'm the only one who can bridge the gap between the old ways and whatever is coming. does that sound crazy to you?",
